So, since last year nunchi meme pages chala ekkuva ayyayi. Whether the reason be it lockdown, or the false hope of Fame and money through meme pages. 
Meme pages aithe unnayi Kani, manchi memes aithe levu. Few people have messaged me asking "meme page create chesamu, memes ela cheyali cheppandi bro". Memes ela cheyali teliyakapote meme page enduku create chesav, andaka edhaina meme Page lo work cheyachu ga, editor ga or something like that. 
.
Meme pages ki konni avasram Ainavi unnayi, and are in no particular order:
1. Creativity 2. Originality 3. Idea 4. Template(synced) 5. Ability to convey idea in words  6. Follower base.

Meme makers ki content koratha undadhu. Typical memer year content idhe. 
Jan lo new year memes, new year, old daridram. Bhogi pata vastuvula padeyadam,  Sankranthi memes; Jan ending, Feb starting Antha appude January ayipoyindha.. tarvata valentine's weeks meedha(singles vs committed), Feb ending ki malla Rendu nelalu bega ayipoyaya... April beginning lo waiting for IPL ani, april-May lo IPL memes, May end lo IPL ayyindhi, em cheyali ardam kavatledhu, may -june lo summer memes, mid June lo school clg start memes, Sept - Oct lo BB memes, Nov  ki year end em chestunnam, Dec lo Christmas memes, year end, daridram stays memes. Idhi kaaka padndagala ki boledu content. Ramzan ki Muslim friend daggara biryani addukovadam, ugadi ki Hindu friend daggara ugadi pachadi addukovadam, Christmas ki christian friend daggara cake addukovadam. Birthday ki party memes, job leni vaalaki relatives pette ibbandhi, kotha cinema teasers trailers posts, release ki release meedha memes, review memes. Bestie memes, Akka/chelli vanta memes, Penta memes, rotta memes, rotta rotta rotta... Intha rotta Chetta content schedule Unnadhi year Antha rotta tho Chetta spread cheyadaniki, intha Chetta lo kuda memes ni Inka Chetta ga cheseyvallaki naa joharu.. 
I digress... But coming back, intha content undhi year Antha, content koratha ledhu, it's using your creativity and your originality to convey these overused content to put yourselves ahead of others. Same memes padi pages vestaru, Kani padi pages lo muggurulo originality

This is a situation I didn't like to face.

Naa templates andariki easy ga dorakali ani hahstags vadadam start chesa. Kani infact, now hahstags anni corrupt chesaru. Venky, Brahmanandam, trending Templates, pokiri, and much more are basically useless. Nenu vesinavvi 70-80 posts unte, andulo 1000+ memes untayi. This basically makes it really hard for memers to find Templates.
Konni sarlu chiraaku vesi meme eh veyyadam manestunnaru kondaru. Or they simply ask me, but why should they?

Kondaru ah hashtags vadithe reach vastadhi anukuntaaru; well, let's all take a minute to laugh at them. 🤣🤣🤣 Reach hahstags valla chinadi vastadhi, but the bulk comes from your memes and your content. If you content is shit, which is mostly the case. Ah hashtags lo konni "memes", memes eh kaavu. They are absolute trash. So, content change cheyandi, followers tho connect avvandi. Trending lo unnavi veyyandi, and finally regular ga post cheyandi. If you wanna increase your reach, atleast oka logical structure pettukondi, cheekatilo banam visiri toorpu tirigi devuda nuvve dikku ani edavakandi. 

Mari kondaru kavalane chestaru. Enduku antaru? Enduko naaku aithe telidhu, so, vallaki msg chesta teeyamani, usually they either delete the msg request and not respond, lekapothe respond ayyi, Nenu teeyanu, em chesukuntavo chesuko antaru. To those, I just block them right away.

Moodo rakam, anukokunda use chesevaalu. Pokiri meme vesaka # kotti Pokiri ani type chesaka edhi unte adhi tag Chesi mingutaaru. Why? Again, I don't know. 

So, ilanti vaala valla chala memers ki kastam avtundhi. Finding a Template is hard, naa page eh kaadhu, migata template pages kaanivandi, they have a similar problem. Hahstags clean ga unchadam ela?
Ekkuvaga hashtags use Chesina pages ni Block cheyandi. 
Munde idhi chepdam anukunna, kani chala alochinchaka odhu anukunna. Madhyalo chala pages suffer avtai. Anukokunda Okati Rendu sarlu hashtags use Chesina sarey, chala memes ki vesaru emo ani chala Mandi block cheyachu, andukani Nenu mundu cheppaledhu. Ippudu tappatledhu.

Oka meme page ni or insta account ni block cheste, vaala memes/comments/likes, etc. yevi meeku kanipinchavu.

Eeroju tho TKA Start chesi 2 years avutundhi.
Nov 2018 lo kaali ga edho side project ga saradaga start chesina tempaltes_ki_adda ani oka page intha peddadhi avtadhi ani expect cheyaledhu.

I've never envisioned something this big for TKA. Ee Rendu savatsarallo I've met so many people, Chala Mandi friends ayyaru, kondaru Inka close ayyaru. Adhi anta comes back to this small "side project" I've put in..

Initially, 'Rick and Morty' tv series ki fan page la create cheddam anukoni start chesanu ee page. If you see, picklerickmutha ani untadhi naa first ID, and then templates cheddam ani alochana tho switch ayya (along with the already abundant rick and morty fan pages). 
//Also rick and morty chudani vaalu unte chudandi. [WARNING: It's adult animation genre] 

Ee page naaku Chala ne nerpindhi... You can make a family out of strangers ani oka fact nerpindhi. Kastallo unte Sahayam ki vache gunam penchindhi. Alane baadha lo unte cheppukone vyakthulni parichayam chesindhi.
Additionally, Chala mukhyam ainadhi, naalo opika ni penchindhi (along with my OCD)😜. Idhanta page start cheyakunda undi unte kuda develop chesukunevadini emo, Kani pakkaga aithe cheppalenu. 

Entho work pettanu ee page lo, Chala templates vesanu, inkenno movies download chesanu. Telegram channel create chesanu, and akkada Chala templates chesanu, and website kuda start chesanu, and all work I've put in. Page kosam, page followers kosam chesanu..

So, to all those helped me stay afloat these two years, and supported me nevertheless. Thank you 😊 and kottaga vachina vaalaki "Swagatam". 

Hopefully ilane Mee support istu untaru ani aasistunna Mee TKA admin❤️

Sai Kumar gaaru CNR character baaga chesaru. 

Oka one or two illogical scenes vunnay but you won't mind them. 

Prathi episode ki mundu okka scene paduddi. Next level vuntay avi and that endings also next episode mida excitement penchesthay. And deva katta gaari taking loved it. Chaala goppaga thisaru. Series ayyaka oka rendu mudu interviews chusa about this show. He mentioned that mayasabha is like Avengers. I hope he continues this series. 

Too much engaging and I would like to re-watch it again and I am just recommending to go and watch.
